      "html": "\n<div class=\"min-h-[900px] bg-[#050507] text-white font-['Inter'] selection:bg-cyan-500/30 selection:text-cyan-200 p-6 md:p-10 relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"1\">\n\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(0,240,255,0.1)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,240,255,0.1)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:40px_40px]\" data-kid=\"1-1\"></div>\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02] pointer-events-none bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,#00f0ff,transparent_70%)]\" data-kid=\"1-2\"></div>\n<link data-kid=\"1-3\" data-name=\"tabler icon font stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<style data-kid=\"0\">\n    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');\n    \n    .font-space { font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; }\n    .font-mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }\n    \n    .glass-panel {\n      background: rgba(21, 21, 27, 0.4);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);\n      position: relative;\n    }\n    \n    .glass-panel::before {\n      content: '';\n      position: absolute;\n      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;\n      height: 1px;\n      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent);\n    }\n\n    .neon-text-cyan {\n      color: #00f0ff;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);\n    }\n    \n    .neon-text-purple {\n      color: #bd00ff;\n      text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(189, 0, 255, 0.3);\n    }\n\n    .neon-border-cyan {\n      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);\n      box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05);\n    }\n\n    .corner-accent::before, .corner-accent::after {\n      content: '';\n      position: absolute;\n      width: 10px;\n      height: 10px;\n      border-color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.3);\n      pointer-events: none;\n    }\n    .corner-tl::before { top: 0; left: 0; border-top: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-top-left-radius: 12px; }\n    .corner-tr::after { top: 0; right: 0; border-top: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; border-top-right-radius: 12px; }\n    .corner-bl::before { bottom: 0; left: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid; border-left: 1px solid; border-bottom-left-radius: 12px; }\n    .corner-br::after { bottom: 0; right: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid; border-right: 1px solid; border-bottom-right-radius: 12px; }\n\n    .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {\n      width: 4px;\n    }\n    .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n      background: transparent;\n    }\n    .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n      background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.2);\n      border-radius: 10px;\n    }\n\n    @keyframes scanline {\n      0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }\n      100% { transform: translateY(100%); }\n    }\n    .scanline::after {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      inset: 0;\n      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05), transparent);\n      height: 20%;\n      width: 100%;\n      animation: scanline 4s linear infinite;\n      pointer-events: none;\n    }\n  </style>\n\n<header class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"1-4\" data-name=\"main navigation bar\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"1-4-1\" data-name=\"user profile logo container\">\n<div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-1\" data-name=\"hexagon icon\">\n<i class=\"ti ti-hexagons text-cyan-400 text-xl\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-1-1\"></i>\n</div>\n<div data-kid=\"1-4-1-2\" data-name=\"logo text section\">\n<h2 class=\"text-xl font-space font-bold tracking-tight uppercase\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2-1\" data-name=\"brand name\">OE <span class=\"text-cyan-400\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2-1-1\" data-name=\"chess lab brand text\">Chess Lab</span></h2>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2-2\" data-name=\"engine status indicator\">\n<span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2-2-1\" data-name=\"status pulse dot\"></span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"1-4-1-2-2-2\" data-name=\"engine link text\">Engine Link: Stable</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8 glass-panel px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"1-4-2\" data-name=\"performance stats container\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-1\" data-name=\"cpu load stats\">\n<span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-1-1\" data-name=\"cpu load label\">CPU Load</span>\n<span class=\"text-xs font-mono text-cyan-400\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-1-2\" data-name=\"cpu load percentage\">12.4%</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-px h-6 bg-white/10\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-2\" data-name=\"separator line 1\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-3\" data-name=\"latency stats\">\n<span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-3-1\" data-name=\"latency label\">Latency</span>\n<span class=\"text-xs font-mono text-purple-400\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-3-2\" data-name=\"latency value\">22ms</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"w-px h-6 bg-white/10\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-4\" data-name=\"separator line 2\"></div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-5\" data-name=\"depth stats\">\n<span class=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-5-1\" data-name=\"depth label\">Depth</span>\n<span class=\"text-xs font-mono text-white/70\" data-kid=\"1-4-2-5-2\" data-name=\"depth value\">32/50</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"1-4-3\" data-name=\"user account area\">\n<div class=\"text-right\" data-kid=\"1-4-3-1\" data-name=\"user name and id\">\n<p class=\"text-sm font-space font-medium\" data-kid=\"1-4-3-1-1\" data-name=\"user name text\">Grandmaster Alpha</p>\n<p class=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40\" data-kid=\"1-4-3-1-2\" data-name=\"user id text\">ID: 9928-OE-CH</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"relative group\" data-kid=\"1-4-3-2\" data-name=\"avatar container\">\n<img alt=\"User Avatar\" class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-white/10 group-hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"1-4-3-2-1\" data-name=\"user avatar image\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=gm_alpha\">\n<div class=\"absolute -bottom-1 -right-1 w-4 h-4 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 border-2 border-[#050507]\" data-kid=\"1-4-3-2-2\" data-name=\"status badge\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</header>\n\n<main class=\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 relative z-10\" data-kid=\"1-5\" data-name=\"main bento grid layout\">\n\n<section class=\"col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl overflow-hidden min-h-[520px] flex flex-col group scanline corner-accent corner-tl corner-tr corner-bl corner-br\" data-kid=\"1-5-1\" data-name=\"hero progress section\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-1\" data-name=\"hero image background container\">\n<img alt=\"Holographic King\" class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 mix-blend-screen transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-1-1\" data-name=\"holographic king image\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1767972159445-ae8732f0a3a3?auto=format&amp;w=1200&amp;q=80&amp;fit=crop\">\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#050507] via-[#050507]/60 to-transparent\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-1-2\" data-name=\"gradient overlay 1\"></div>\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#050507] via-transparent to-transparent\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-1-3\" data-name=\"gradient overlay 2\"></div>\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_50%,rgba(0,240,255,0.05),transparent)]\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-1-4\" data-name=\"radial gradient overlay\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"relative p-10 flex flex-col h-full justify-between flex-grow\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2\" data-name=\"content text container\">\n<div data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1\" data-name=\"version badge container\">\n<div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-400 text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase mb-8\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1-1\" data-name=\"activity heartbeat icon\">\n<i class=\"ti ti-activity-heartbeat animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1-1-1\"></i>\n            Strategic Analysis Platform v4.0.2\n          </div>\n<h1 class=\"text-7xl font-space font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-2 tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1-2\" data-name=\"hero title\">\n            Progress<br data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1-2-1\" data-name=\"hero title line break\"><span class=\"text-white/30\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1-2-2\" data-name=\"hero title suffix\">Overview</span>\n</h1>\n<p class=\"text-white/50 max-w-md font-space text-lg leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-1-3\" data-name=\"hero subtitle\">\n            Holographic rendering of tactical performance and engine-evaluated growth trajectories.\n          </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex items-end gap-12\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-2\" data-name=\"stats summary row\">\n<div class=\"space-y-2\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-2-1\" data-name=\"elo rating group\">\n<p class=\"text-white/30 text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-2-1-1\" data-name=\"elo rating label\">Elo Rating</p>\n<div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-2\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-2-1-2\" data-name=\"elo rating display\">\n<span class=\"text-7xl font-space font-bold neon-text-cyan\" data-kid=\"1-5-1-2-2-1-2